  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:• Existing recipients using a Baha sound processor on a Softband for at
        least three months

          -  Subjects aged 5 through 12 years of age

          -  Subjects should be able to perform clinical testing adapted for age and developmental
             status, (Threshold sound field audiometry and basic monosyllabic word test, PBK)

          -  Willingness on behalf of the subject's parent or guardian to complete study
             questionnaire

        Exclusion Criteria:• Subject's inability to perform requisite test measures as described in
        the study protocol
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
